      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'M MY DESIGN (7) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Elegant Cindy (20.06) in a TG1-4W. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature in the finish again. COME BACK CANDY (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 342m behind Centre Bounce (20.93) in a TG1-4W. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Shapes as one to consider. RIO HOPE (1) was on speed throughout and overcame a check to finish third (17.19) at Murray Bridge Straight over 300m in a TG1-4W. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. TOUGH COOKIE (4) is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time.",
